name: TheGrandTourQuotes
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: grand tour quotes
des: Enable the skill, then ask Alexa at any time to 'open The Grand Tour Quotes' and she will pick a random quote from the database and share it with you. The quote will come from any of the available to view episodes on Amazon Video. Over 500 quotes to hear!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
